additionalProperty.value: Ingredients: Brown Rice (83%), Rice Bran Oil (contains Antioxidant (307b)), Sesame seeds (including Black Sesame (2.8%)), Cane Sugar, Sea Salt, Onion Powder, Maltodextrin (from Corn),Tamarind Powder, Soy Sauce Powder (contains Soy), Yeast Extract, Emulsifier (from Soy, 322).

additionalProperty.value: Contains Sesame, May Be Present Milk, Contains Soy

description: You've never had a cracker quite like this before-by air baking (yes, using hot air), Peckish have created a thinner, lighter and crispier cracker. This unique way of baking layers of black sesame and whole grain brown rice is what creates the perfect crunch and lightness in each flavourful bite.
name: Brown Rice Black Sesame Crackers
